## 5. Layout Managers

| Manager | When to Use | Example |
|---------|-------------|---------|
| `FlowLayout` | Simple leftâ€‘toâ€‘right flow | `new FlowLayout()` |
| `BorderLayout` | Five regions (N, S, E, W, C) | `new BorderLayout()` |
