## 7. Custom Painting

Override `paint(Graphics g)` in a `Canvas` or `Component`:

```java
class MyCanvas extends Canvas {
    public void paint(Graphics g) {
        g.setColor(Color.BLUE);
        g.fillRect(10, 10, 100, 50);
        g.setColor(Color.BLACK);
        g.drawString("Hello AWT!", 20, 40);
    }
}
```

**Remember:** For smoother graphics, use `Graphics2D` (cast `Graphics` to `Graphics2D`).

